      "citation_id": "[CITATION_2]",
      "span_text": "In addition, one in vivo microdialysis study  has shown that local infusion of LEV decreases stimulated but not basal neurotransmitter release in a concentration-dependent manner in the medial PFC. Further studies measuring the effects of systemic LEV on neurotransmitter release using microdialysis or microvoltammetry in the NAc and other reward-relevant targets will be informative in this regard."
